      • getWaypoints

        public java.util.List<DirectionsFeature> getWaypoints()
        A List of DirectionsFeature objects representing intermediate waypoints along route, if any exist. If you request directions with more then two waypoints (origin and destination) addition information about those intermediate points will be given here in a List object.
        Returns:
        List of DirectionsFeature objects.

      • getRoutes

        public java.util.List<DirectionsRoute> getRoutes()
        List containing all the different route options. It's ordered by descending recommendation rank. In other words, object 0 in the List is the highest recommended route. if you setAlternatives to false (default is true) in your builder this should always be a List of size 1.
        Returns:
        List of DirectionsRoute objects.
        Since:
        1.0.0
